labels.name: P2: Fix can wait a while

data.short_description: Trying to delete a voice channel you have manage channel permissions to but not connect permissions to doesn't delete it.
data.steps_to_repro: - Be in a server that you have manage channels permissions in but are not the server owner. - Create a voice channel that you do not have permission to join. - Right click it (or go into the full settings modal) and try to delete it.
